<h2 class="blog--title">
<a href="/blog/2007/04/10/spring-framework-2-0-4-released">Spring Framework 2.0.4 Released</a>
</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
<div class="meta-data--item desktop-only">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon releases"></div>
<a class="category" href="/blog/category/releases">Releases</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<img class="meta-data--icon" src="https://gravatar.com/avatar/ba9686d8c567aabedc1b7f8b6a7fb3d6?s=20&amp;d=mm" />
<a class="author" href="/team/jhoeller">Juergen Hoeller</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon calendar"></div>
<time class="date" pubdate="" datetime="2007-04-10 19:01:00.0">April 10, 2007</time>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon comments"></div>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="984" href="/blog/2007/04/10/spring-framework-2-0-4-released#disqus_thread">
</a></div>
</header>
<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p></p>
<p align="left"> Dear Spring Community,</p>
<p align="left">We are pleased to announce that Spring 2.0.4 has been released.&nbsp; This is a bugfix and enhancement release, addressing all reported bugs against the Spring 2.0 series and introducing significant performance improvements.&nbsp; We recommend upgrading to Spring 2.0.4 from previous 2.0.x releases.</p>
<p align="center"><img border="0" src="http://static.springframework.org/images/spring20.png" alt="Spring 2.0 Released" title="Spring 2.0 Released"></p>
<div align="center">
<a target="_blank" href="https://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=73357&amp;package_id=173644&amp;release_id=500032">Download</a> |
<a target="_blank" href="http://static.springframework.org/spring/docs/2.0.4/reference/index.html">Documentation</a> |
<a target="_blank" href="http://static.springframework.org/spring/docs/2.0.4/changelog.txt">Changelog</a>
</div>
<div align="center">
&nbsp;
</div>
<p>Regarding the performance improvements, repeated creation of Spring bean instances is up to <strong>12 times faster</strong> in this release than previous versions of Spring 2.0. AspectJ-based weaving performance has also increased by a significant factor. <br></p>
</div>
</section>
<a class="blog-preview--readmore desktop-only" href="/blog/2007/04/10/spring-framework-2-0-4-released">
Read more...
</a>
</article>
